	<string id="st_wpn_g36nimble_rwap">
		<text>G36C "Merc"</text>
	</string>
	<string id="st_wpn_g36nimble_rwap_descr">
		<text>Created to replace the aging G3, the G36 continues to set the standard in the field of assault rifles with unprecedented reliability. Lightweight, accurate and simple in maintenance, it has found its way into the hands of various law enforcement agencies worldwide. The 'C' model features a shorter barrel, handguard and stock and includes a flash hider.\n
		This variant comes with a foregrip, laser sight and modified bolt for an increased rate of fire.\n \n
		%c[pda_white]PROPERTIES:\n
		%c[d_cyan] • %c[pda_white] Origin: %c[ui_gray_2]Germany\n
		%c[d_cyan] • %c[pda_white] Manufacturer: %c[ui_gray_2]Heckler &amp; Koch\n
		</text>
	</string>

